<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Psalmopoeus chronoarachne sp. nov. female holotype (ZSFQ-i 11704), spermatheca A dorsal view B ventral view C apical view. Abbreviation: iLB, ill-defined lobe. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951937" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Psalmopoeus ecclesiasticus non-type female (QCAZ-i 274322), spermatheca A dorsal view B ventral view. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951946" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Distribution of the genus Psalmopoeus Pocock, 1895 in Ecuador, including biogeographical regions of Ecuador. White star = Reserva Otongachi, type locality of P. satanas sp. nov.; White triangle = Localities of P. satanas sp. nov. paratypes; Black star = Hacienda La Mariela, type locality of P. chronoarachne; Yellow star = Rio Sapayo, type locality of P. ecclesiasticus; Yellow circle = Carondelet, historical record of P. ecclesiasticus; Yellow squares = Additional records of P. ecclesiasticus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951947" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Distribution of the genus Psalmopoeus Pocock, 1895 in Ecuador, including mining concessions and cropland use. White star = Reserva Otongachi, type locality of P. satanas sp. nov.; White triangle = localities of P. satanas sp. nov. paratypes; black star = Hacienda La Mariela, type locality of P. chronoarachne; yellow star = Rio Sapayo, type locality of P. ecclesiasticus; yellow circle = Carondelet, historical record of P. ecclesiasticus; yellow squares = additional records of P. ecclesiasticus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951948" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Psalmopoeus satanas sp. nov. male holotype (ZSFQ-i 12150), palpal bulb (right hand side), arrow indicates ventral dilatation of embolus A prolateral view B retrolateral view C dorsal view D ventral view. Scale bars: 1.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951940" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Psalmopoeus satanas sp. nov. male holotype (ZSFQ-i 12150), tibial apophysis (left hand side) A retrolateral view B dorsal view C dorso-retrolateral view D prolateral view. Scale bars: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951941" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Psalmopoeus satanas sp. nov. male holotype (ZSFQ-i 12150), live habitus A dorsolateral view B dorsal view. Scale bars: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951942" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Psalmopoeus satanas sp. nov. Maxillae showing maxillary lyra A male holotype (ZSFQ-i 12150) (right hand side) B female paratype (QCAZ-i 274324) (left side). Scale bars: 0.4 mm (A), 0.2 mm (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951943" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Psalmopoeus satanas sp. nov. female paratype (QCAZ-i 274324), spermatheca A dorsal view B ventral view. Abbreviations: iLB, ill-defined lobe; wLB, well-defined lobe. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/951944" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.108991.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Psalmopoeus satanas sp. nov. female paratype, habitus and previous examinator labels. Scale bar: 15 mm." ;
